Melba Moore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melba_Moore 0 Beatrice Melba Hill (born October 29, 1945), known by her stage name, Melba Moore is an American singer, actress, voice actress, and entertainer. Moore is the daughter of saxophonist Teddy Hill and R singer Bonnie Davis.
